\id PHM - Mpoto Bible Version
\h Filimoni
\toc1 Baluwa jaka Paulo kwaka Filimoni
\toc2 Filimoni
\toc3 Fili
\mt2 Baluwa jaka Paulo kwaka
\mt1 Filimoni
\imt1 Ulongulelo
\ip Chitabu chenjenu chekibhi chijipi chakalembakiki na Mtumi Paulo (Sula 1:1). Paulo akabhi muchifungo chikahi paalembika baluwa jenu, lijambu linyahi nde kubha iwezikana akabhi mu muchi wa Loma chikahi paakachilembike. Na ngati nde chakaka akabhi ku Loma chikahi paachilembikaje, bhela iwezikana nakanopi kubha chitabu chenu chakalembakiki mu chaka cha 61 baada ja kubhelakeka Yesu Kristo. Na chitabu cha Bhakolosai nachombi chakalembakiki mu chikahi chenihechi.
\ip Paulo akundembi baluwa jenu mundu jumu joakalowakiki Filimoni. Filimoni akabhi mundu wa likanisa kabhete akabhi na ntumwa waki. Paulo akundembi baluwa jenu Filimoni nahuli kunjopa ngaandapu mtumwa waki Onesimo joakabhi antiliki kunyuma hoku. Kwa shelia ja Kiloma, Filimoni akabhi na lujiniku lwa kunkoma Onesimo. Paulo atumi malobhi gha kumpembalela na kunjeghe mtima Filimoni anjetakya Onesimo ngati ndongu waki muka Kristo, na hata apwagha kubha anjetakalya kubha muhenga lihengu papamu naku Paulo mweni (Sula 1:13-14).
\iot Ghaghabhihomu
\io1 Paulo andamuki Filimoni (Sula 1:1-3).
\io1 Paulo abhoha lilobhu kwa ndandi jaka Onesimo kubha Filimoni anjetakya ngati ndongu waki muka Kristo (Sula 1:4-21).
\io1 Paulo ajomule baluwa jaki kwa kulanda ghala ghaaghapala kwa kunjendela Filimoni na kubhoa ulamukilu (Sula 1:22-25).
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nepani Paulo, mkongeka kwa ndandi jaka Yesu Kristo, papamu na Timoseo ndongu witu,
\p Tukulembe wa Filimoni umpalu witu, na muhenga lihengu papamu na tepani,
\v 2 na likanisa lokapi lelihimangana munyumba jaku, na ndombu witu Afia, na linjolinjoli njitu Alikipo:
\p 
\v 3 Chihomu na chibya kwinu, na lukwali yeihuma kwaka Chapanga Atati witu, na kwaka Bambo Yesu Kristo.
\s1 Upalu na uhobhalelu waka Filimoni
\p 
\v 4 Machobha ghokapi nunchengu Chapanga wangu, panukukomboka mu malobhu ghangu.
\v 5 Kwa ndandi nyowini malobhi gha uhobhalelu waku kwaka Bambo Yesu na upalu waku kwa bhahuhu bhokapi.
\v 6 Nukulobhela kwaka Chapanga nahuli uhobhalelu hoghu ghoushiliki papamu na tepani kwaka Chapanga uweza kujingila mkati nakanopi na uweza kubha na umanyi wamaheli nakanopi wa mbengalelu yokapi yetuipata kwa kulombana kwitu na Kristo Yesu.
\v 7 Undongu wangu, upalu waku unetili chiheku chikolongwa na kunyeghela mtima namaa! Kwa ndandi ujihekihi mitima ja bhahuhu.
\s1 Paulo andobha Filimoni anjopalya Onesimo
\p 
\v 8 Bhela, nepani ngati ndongu waku kwa kulombana na Kristo nakabya nhweziki kubha na ukangamalu wa kukulaghalakila ghala ghaghukupalika kutenda,
\v 9 nambu kwa ndandi ja upalu nde wichu nukulobhaje, ndenda bhenibhela hata ngati nepani Paulo nde nunseja, na sajenu mkongeka waka Yesu Kristo bhelabhela.
\v 10 Bhela, nukulobha unjopalya mwana wangu Onesimo, ambaju nde mwana wangu kwa kulombana na Kristo, chikahi panakabhi ngongakiki muchifungo.
\v 11 Onesimo jolajola ambaju pamwande akabhi ngacheapalika kwaku wehapa hata pachokope, nambu sajenu akupalika wehapa na nepani bhelabhela.
\p 
\v 12 Sajenu nunkelabhu kabhete kwaku, najombi nde ngati mtima wangu namwete.
\v 13 Nakapaliki atamaje na nepani pambane, nahuli akamulaje pandu paku pa kunyangatila chikahi chenu nakabya muchifungu kwa ndandi ja kutangaza Malobhi Manyahi.
\v 14 Nambu ngachembala kutenda lijambu lokapi lela panga kujetanganela na wehapa, nahuli wambone wokapi ghoutenda ngawikubha wa kujomalakela, nambu kwa kupala wamwete.
\p 
\v 15 Maghambu pangi nde ndandi Onesimo akatami kutali na wehapa kwa chikahi kichokopi, nahuli akelabhuka kabhete kwaku na kutama naku mileli.
\v 16 Na sajenu jombi nga mtumwa kabhete, nambu jombi nde wamboni nakanopi jaka mtumwa. Sajenu jombi nde ndongu witu mpalu kwa kulombana na Kristo. Jombi akambaliki nepani, na anaakupala wehapa nakanope, ndandi jombi nde ngati mtumwa na ndongu witu muka Bambo!
\p 
\v 17 Bhela, anangati umanya nepani kubha nundongu waku, unjopalya kabhete ngati bhela ukabya unyopalela nepani namwete.
\v 18 Na ngati akuhokihi kwa lijambu lokapi lela au anaundai chokapi chela, unaya nepani.
\v 19 Nepani Paulo nemba namwete kwa chiwoku changu, nepani ananukulepaje. Ngachembwagha kubha wehapa ubhi na lideni la kunepa nepani matamu ghaku.
\v 20 Bhela, undongu wangu, ndokulela kupata nyonjeka kwaku kwa ndandi ja lihina laka Bambo, unhekihaje mtima wangu ngati undongu muka Kristo!
\p 
\v 21 Nemba koni nakahobhalya kubha anaunyetakalyaje lilobhu langu, kabhete manyi kubha anautendaje hata nakanopi ja ghanukujopiki hagha.
\v 22 Na papamu na ghanihagha, umekila wichu pandu pa kughonela, maghambu nhobhale kubha kwa malobhu ghinu, Chapanga anaaneta konihoku.
\s1 Malamukilu gha kujomulela
\p 
\v 23 Epafra, joabhi mkongeka njangu kwa ndandi ja kuntumaki Kristo Yesu, akulamukila.
\v 24 Bhelabhela Mako, Alistako, Dema na Luka, bhahenga lihengu bhajangu bhukulamukila.
\p 
\v 25 Chihomu chaka Bambo witu Yesu Kristo chibya papamu na roho hinu. Amina.
